data.description: Come see this Property! It is located on a huge corner lot. It is the perfect place to build a backyard oasis. This home offers 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, spacious kitchen, and a spacious dining room. It has a new roof that was replaced in 2022, and a new water heater and furnace that were replaced in 2023. It is also conveniently located near a creek where you can fish and enjoy the great outdoors. It is also located near the Gemini Giant. This home could use a little TLC and will be sold AS-IS, however, it has a great floor concept and so much potential.
